{"tid":2115770,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"求救！如何令自己更有動力","createTime":"2020-07-19T17:59:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T16:46:27.000Z","uid":25440,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"df0900db454e74caf32c69f277aad89cfc91eb6a","tid":2115770,"uid":25440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T17:59:52.000Z","msg":"就快面對人生中好重要嘅考試 <br />\n但仍然唔夠自信同埋動力去面對<br />\n有咩方法令自己更有動力 、幹勁<br />\n求分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa9252ff6dd055ab647df2b7cbfb3faefdea7897","tid":2115770,"uid":281775,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T20:28:12.000Z","msg":"冇動力乜野先？<br />\n你冇動力拿起書去溫與溫極都唔識再冇動力繼續 已經係兩件事<br />\n你反思下自己係如何？形容下？這些都已經可以幫你更認識自己"},{"pid":"f5a453ebe4014a440f7e1f5ae5eac9a0ff3fd074","tid":2115770,"uid":281775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T20:29:39.000Z","msg":"有些人係deadline fighter <br />\n你係唔係？"},{"pid":"ed5d1ef9c0bee83ceadee661302e0fe4113aa1a4","tid":2115770,"uid":25440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa9252ff6dd055ab647df2b7cbfb3faefdea7897","tid":2115770,"uid":281775,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T20:28:12.000Z","msg":"冇動力乜野先？<br />\n你冇動力拿起書去溫與溫極都唔識再冇動力繼續 已經係兩件事<br />\n你反思下自己係如何？形容下？這些都已經可以幫你更認識自己"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T11:03:30.000Z","msg":"both <br />\n今年都有種消極面對所有野嘅態度<br />\n心裡面一直有個諗法&mdash;「失敗就轉行」，可能就係呢個諗法害死我<br />\n我好想改變呀 但控制唔到自己咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc663690de90e0928a92add3d023cd547370d3e","tid":2115770,"uid":25440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5a453ebe4014a440f7e1f5ae5eac9a0ff3fd074","tid":2115770,"uid":281775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T20:29:39.000Z","msg":"有些人係deadline fighter <br />\n你係唔係？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-2